#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.ceil:2
msgid "Return the ceiling of the input, element-wise."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.ceil:4
msgid ""
"The ceil of the scalar `x` is the smallest integer `i`, such that ``i >= "
"x``.  It is often denoted as :math:`\\lceil x \\rceil`."
msgstr ""

